---
const { names } = Astro.props;
---

<section class="section interview-section" id="interviews">
  <div class="section-head compact">
    <p class="section-kicker">Interviews / 重要訪談對象</p>
    <h2><span data-zh>跨科技、創業、金融與生醫的全球觀察</span><span data-en>Global perspective across technology, entrepreneurship, finance, and biomedicine</span></h2>
    <p><span data-zh>以下名單依英文 Bio 建立；呈現重點是專業觀察範圍，而非名人堆疊。</span><span data-en>The list is sourced from the English bio and framed as a map of Anita's reporting range.</span></p>
  </div>
  <div class="interviewee-grid">
    {names.map((person) => (
      <article class="interviewee-card">
        <h3>{person.name}</h3>
        <p><span data-zh>{person.title_zh}</span><span data-en>{person.title_en}</span></p>
      </article>
    ))}
  </div>
</section>
